Title: On $U_V(1)\times U_A(1)$ gauge invariance in a Lorentz-violating QED
Authors: M. A. Anacleto and F. A. Brito and E. Passos
Abstract: We introduce a Lorentz-symmetry violating master quantum electrodynamics which preserves the $U_V(1)\times U_A(1)$ gauge symmetry. The master fermionic sector can radiatively induce a master effective action which simultaneously displays the same electromagnetic terms present in the Carroll-Field-Jackiw, Myers-Pospelov and Aether actions.
